	    <div class="row ceg-t35">
	        <div class="large-9 small-10 large-centered small-centered column">
	            <p class="ceg-b32">From pre-planned events celebrating the new addition to your household to impromptu invites you simply must attend, special occasions can rule your social calendar during pregnancy. As with all things, preparation is key. Step away from the sweatpants and T-shirt and follow our handy guide on what special occasion <a href="{{ENV_HOSTNAME}}/shop/womens-clothing/maternity-clothes/Department_type/Dresses?id=66718">maternity dress</a> to wear where.</p>
	        </div>

	        <div class="large-9 small-10 large-centered small-centered column">
	        	<h5>What To Wear To My Gender Reveal Party?</h5>
	            <p class="ceg-b32">Gender reveal parties have gained momentum over the years and we're always down for another reason to celebrate. For your outfit, consider a dress that is stylish at any stage. An A-line or a fit-and-flare dress is perfect for pregnancy, especially since these dresses can feature elasticized waistlines, flowing silhouettes and self-tie belts that highlight your bump.</p>
	        </div>

	        <div class="large-9 small-10 large-centered small-centered column">
	        	<h5>What To Wear To My Babymoon?</h5>
	            <p class="ceg-b32">If you're able to take a couple’s vacation during your pregnancy (aka a babymoon), then do it in style! Make you (and your bump) the center of attention with a wonderful dress. A flowing maxi or short baby doll dress is as effortless as it is flattering. Sleeveless dresses are perfect for layering and warm weather. This piece can flatter throughout pregnancy and can easily be paired with a cardigan or blazer if you’re traveling somewhere chillier or want to wear it later. Don’t forget a <a href="{{ENV_HOSTNAME}}/shop/b/maternity-swimwear?id=128857">maternity swimsuit</a> if you plan to be near water.</p>
	        </div>

	        <div class="large-9 small-10 large-centered small-centered column">
	        	<h5>What To Wear To An Engagement Party/Wedding</h5>
	            <p class="ceg-b32">Vow to wow the crowd at an engagement party or wedding with a cocktail dress, sans cocktail and heavy on the lace. Achieve haute mama status with a midi length dress that’s both demure and daring. Stick with a classic formal color palette of jewel tones and timeless black.</p>
	        </div>

	        <div class="large-9 small-10 large-centered small-centered column">
	        	<h5>What To Wear To A Birthday Party?</h5>
	            <p class="ceg-b32">Whether you're celebrating your birthday or someone else’s, you need to look the part. A sundress in a pretty print is a casual stunner. For a more dressed up appearance, go with a timeless shift dress.</p>
